### About 

Phronesis is a government contracting and consulting firm working in the area of defense, finance, and compliance. We provide web enabled tools for big data processing, scalable machine learning and statistics, text analytics, and data exploration/visualization.

### Contact

For questions or consultations please email casey@gophronesis.com
